Package org.hkijena.acaq5.ui.events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlgorithmEvent
    An event around ACAQAlgorithmUI
    AlgorithmFinderSuccessEvent
    Generated when the algorithm finder successfully found a connection
    AlgorithmSelectedEvent
    Generated when an algorithm is selected
    AlgorithmSelectionChangedEvent
    Triggered when An ACAQAlgorithmGraphCanvasUI selection was changed
    AlgorithmUIActionRequestedEvent
    An action that is requested by an ACAQAlgorithmUI and passed down to a ACAQAlgorithmGraphEditorUI
    DefaultAlgorithmUIActionRequestedEvent
    Triggered when an ACAQAlgorithmUI requests a default action (double click)
    RunUIWorkerFinishedEvent
    Generated when an ACAQRunWorker finished its work
    RunUIWorkerInterruptedEvent
    Generated when work of an ACAQRunWorker is interrupted
    RunUIWorkerProgressEvent
    Generated when an ACAQRunWorker reports progress
    RunUIWorkerStartedEvent
    Generated when an ACAQRunWorker was started
